{"id":"herod-antipas","term":"Herod Antipas","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Herod’s son by Malthace (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Matthew 14:1\">Matt. 14:1</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 3:1\">Luke 3:1</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 1:19\">19</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 9:7\">9:7</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Acts 13:1\">Acts 13:1</a>). (See ANTIPAS.)</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Matthew 14:1","Luke 3:1","Genesis 1:19","Genesis 9:7","Acts 13:1"]}